{"tid":1512112,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"instagram share 反送中運動新聞唔見咁勤力","createTime":"2019-08-27T17:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T21:09:51.000Z","uid":13385,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fd1ce82ccc4a4642a831c4f3bf9b3288222ef04e","tid":1512112,"uid":13385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:57:02.000Z","msg":"share嗰個亞馬遜森林大火 有$1 donate 就咁落力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIG見倒啲對反送中運動冇表態嘅人<br />\n但呢幾日 就SHARE個乜鬼 亞馬遜森林大火捐款post<br />\n亞馬遜森林大火係大新聞<br />\n之但係而家香港仲撚大火呀 屌你地班平衡時空撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即使係和理非嘅 <br />\n都出黎集下會, 遊下行, 做下冷空軍師, share下唔同有關我地屋企 香港嘅新聞落力啲仲好啦  <br />\n<br />\n唔係話你地唔表態就唔支持反送中<br />\n但見你班平衡時空撚 share個亞馬遜森林 都唔share反送中真係炆炆地<br />\n<br />\n利伸 唔分化 和理非"},{"pid":"12ea06614da1565d81c85ca1e431165f63e50510","tid":1512112,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T17:58:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新post！<br />\n更upmdate！ 求幫推！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士進程請入，一個也不能少不是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9f90f0f87ffcc4e1f64ab8f6d929abc76bcb5d93","tid":1512112,"uid":221743,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:01:49.000Z","msg":"如果地球收咗皮 香港有真普選都冇用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"0430507cd344d8f0e78b952357dd1c6501e7f508","tid":1512112,"uid":101110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:13:26.000Z","msg":"都share咗三個月<br />\n其實地球都好重要"},{"pid":"2582d2e8600d33ef32d8d70a4e3a277c42f78265","tid":1512112,"uid":304366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"